<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="<%= lang %>">
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title><%= lang === 'ru' ? 'Редактор формул LaTeX — Пишите физические уравнения с предпросмотром' : 'LaTeX Equation Editor — Write Physics Equations with Live Preview' %> | Savchenko Solutions</title>
    <meta name="description" content="<%= lang === 'ru' ? 'Бесплатный онлайн-редактор формул LaTeX с предпросмотром MathJax. Шаблоны для распространённых физических уравнений: законы Ньютона, уравнения Максвелла, уравнение Шрёдингера и другие.' : 'Free online LaTeX equation editor with live MathJax preview. Includes templates for common physics equations: Newton\'s laws, Maxwell\'s equations, Schrodinger equation, and more.' %>" />
    <link rel="canonical" href="https://savchenkosolutions.com/<%= lang %>/tools/latex" />

    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet" />
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=STIX+Two+Math&display=swap" rel="stylesheet" />
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/design-system.css" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/main_page.css" />
    <link rel="icon" type="image/svg+xml" href="/img/logo.svg" />
    <link rel="icon" type="image/png" href="/img/logo.png" />
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>

    <script type="application/ld+json">
    {
        "@context": "https://schema.org",
        "@type": "WebApplication",
        "name": "<%= lang === 'ru' ? 'Редактор формул LaTeX' : 'LaTeX Equation Editor' %>",
        "description": "<%= lang === 'ru' ? 'Бесплатный онлайн-редактор формул LaTeX с предпросмотром MathJax. Шаблоны для распространённых физических уравнений.' : 'Free online LaTeX equation editor with live MathJax preview. Includes templates for common physics equations.' %>",
        "url": "https://savchenkosolutions.com/<%= lang %>/tools/latex",
        "applicationCategory": "EducationalApplication",
        "operatingSystem": "Any",
        "offers": {
            "@type": "Offer",
            "price": "0",
            "priceCurrency": "USD"
        },
        "isPartOf": {
            "@type": "WebSite",
            "name": "Savchenko Solutions",
            "url": "https://savchenkosolutions.com"
        }
    }
    </script>
    <script src="/js/analytics.js"></script>

    <script>
    MathJax = {
      tex: {
        inlineMath: [['$', '$'], ['\\(', '\\)']],
        displayMath: [['$$', '$$'], ['\\[', '\\]']],
        processEscapes: true
      },
      options: {
        skipHtmlTags: ['script', 'noscript', 'style', 'textarea', 'pre', 'code']
      }
    };
    </script>
    <script id="MathJax-script" async src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/mathjax@3/es5/tex-chtml.js"></script>
    <script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/html2canvas/1.4.1/html2canvas.min.js"></script>

    <style>
        .latex-container {
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 1rem 1rem 2rem;
        }
        .latex-header {
            margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
        }
        .latex-header h1 {
            font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
            font-size: 28px;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #2d2d2d;
            margin: 0 0 0.25rem;
        }
        .latex-header p {
            color: #6c757d;
            font-size: 15px;
            margin: 0;
        }

        /* Template button rows */
        .template-section {
            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
        }
        .template-section-label {
            font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
            font-size: 12px;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #6c757d;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.5px;
            margin-bottom: 0.3rem;
        }
        .template-buttons {
            display: flex;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            gap: 4px;
        }
        .template-btn {
            font-family: 'STIX Two Math', 'Cambria Math', serif;
            font-size: 15px;
            padding: 3px 10px;
            background: #f8f9fa;
            border: 1px solid #dee2e6;
            border-radius: 6px;
            color: #2d2d2d;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: border-color 0.15s;
            white-space: nowrap;
            line-height: 1.4;
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            vertical-align: middle;
        }
        .template-btn:hover {
            border-color: #1a1a2e;
            background: #eef1f5;
        }
        .template-btn.physics-btn {
            background: #eef2ff;
        }
        .template-btn.physics-btn:hover {
            border-color: #1a1a2e;
            background: #dde5ff;
        }

        /* Editor panels */
        .editor-panels {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
            gap: 0.75rem;
            margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
        }
        @media (max-width: 767px) {
            .editor-panels {
                grid-template-columns: 1fr;
            }
        }

        .panel-label {
            font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
            font-size: 13px;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #6c757d;
            margin-bottom: 0.3rem;
        }

        #latexInput {
            width: 100%;
            min-height: 200px;
            font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
            font-size: 14px;
            border: 1px solid #dee2e6;
            border-radius: 6px;
            padding: 1rem;
            resize: vertical;
            outline: none;
            color: #2d2d2d;
            background: #fff;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }
        #latexInput:focus {
            border-color: #1a1a2e;
        }
        #latexInput::placeholder {
            color: #adb5bd;
        }

        .preview-panel {
            background: #fff;
            border: 1px solid #dee2e6;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 1rem;
            min-height: 200px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            overflow-x: auto;
        }
        .preview-panel .MathJax_Display {
            margin: 0 !important;
        }
        #previewContent {
            width: 100%;
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 18px;
            color: #2d2d2d;
            word-break: break-word;
        }
        .preview-placeholder {
            color: #adb5bd;
            font-size: 14px;
            font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
        }

        /* Action buttons */
        .action-buttons {
            display: flex;
            gap: 0.5rem;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
        }
        .action-btn {
            font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
            font-size: 13px;
            font-weight: 500;
            padding: 0 16px;
            height: 36px;
            background: #1a1a2e;
            color: #fff;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 6px;
            cursor: pointer;
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 6px;
            transition: opacity 0.15s;
        }
        .action-btn:hover {
            opacity: 0.9;
        }
        .action-btn:disabled {
            opacity: 0.5;
            cursor: not-allowed;
        }
        .action-btn svg {
            width: 14px;
            height: 14px;
            fill: none;
            stroke: currentColor;
            stroke-width: 2;
            stroke-linecap: round;
            stroke-linejoin: round;
        }

        .copy-feedback {
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #27ae60;
            font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
            margin-left: 4px;
            opacity: 0;
            transition: opacity 0.2s;
        }
        .copy-feedback.visible {
            opacity: 1;
        }

        /* Button groups for categorization */
        .template-group {
            display: flex;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            gap: 4px;
            align-items: stretch;
        }
        .template-group + .template-group {
            padding-left: 10px;
            border-left: 1px solid #e9ecef;
        }
        .template-group-label {
            font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
            font-size: 10px;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #adb5bd;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 0.3px;
            align-self: center;
            padding-right: 2px;
            white-space: nowrap;
        }
        @media (max-width: 767px) {
            .template-group + .template-group {
                padding-left: 0;
                border-left: none;
            }
        }

        /* Symbols section (full-width inline) */
        .symbols-section {
            border: 1px solid #dee2e6;
            border-radius: 8px;
            background: #fff;
            overflow: hidden;
        }
        .symbols-header {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            background: #f8f9fa;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #dee2e6;
        }
        .symbols-tabs {
            display: flex;
            flex: 1;
            overflow-x: auto;
        }
        .symbols-tab {
            font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
            font-size: 12px;
            font-weight: 500;
            padding: 6px 10px;
            background: none;
            border: none;
            border-bottom: 2px solid transparent;
            color: #6c757d;
            cursor: pointer;
            white-space: nowrap;
        }
        .symbols-tab:hover {
            color: #2d2d2d;
        }
        .symbols-tab.active {
            color: #1a1a2e;
            border-bottom-color: #1a1a2e;
        }
        .symbols-collapse-btn {
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            width: 32px;
            height: 32px;
            background: none;
            border: none;
            border-left: 1px solid #dee2e6;
            color: #6c757d;
            cursor: pointer;
            flex-shrink: 0;
            transition: color 0.15s;
        }
        .symbols-collapse-btn:hover {
            color: #1a1a2e;
        }
        .symbols-collapse-btn svg {
            transition: transform 0.2s;
        }
        .symbols-section.collapsed .symbols-collapse-btn svg {
            transform: rotate(180deg);
        }
        .symbols-section.collapsed .symbols-grid-wrap {
            display: none;
        }
        .symbols-section.collapsed .symbols-header {
            border-bottom: none;
        }
        .symbols-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(38px, 1fr));
            gap: 3px;
            padding: 6px;
            max-height: 132px;
            overflow-y: auto;
        }
        .symbol-btn {
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            width: 38px;
            height: 38px;
            font-family: 'STIX Two Math', serif;
            font-size: 19px;
            background: #fff;
            border: 1px solid #eee;
            border-radius: 4px;
            color: #2d2d2d;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: background 0.1s, border-color 0.1s;
        }
        .symbol-btn:hover {
            background: #eef1f5;
            border-color: #1a1a2e;
        }

        /* Back link */
        .back-link {
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 4px;
            font-size: 13px;
            color: #6c757d;
            text-decoration: none;
            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
        }
        .back-link:hover {
            color: #1a1a2e;
        }
        .back-link svg {
            width: 14px;
            height: 14px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <%- include('../default/main_site_header') %>

    <div class="latex-container">
        <a href="/<%= lang %>/tools" class="back-link">
            <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
                <polyline points="15 18 9 12 15 6"></polyline>
            </svg>
            <%= lang === 'ru' ? 'Все инструменты' : 'All Tools' %>
        </a>

        <div class="latex-header">
            <h1><%= lang === 'ru' ? 'Редактор формул LaTeX' : 'LaTeX Equation Editor' %></h1>
            <p><%= lang === 'ru' ? 'Пишите физические уравнения с предпросмотром MathJax. Нажмите на шаблон, чтобы вставить его.' : 'Write physics equations with live MathJax preview. Click a template to insert it.' %></p>
        </div>

        <div class="template-section">
            <div class="template-buttons" id="mathTemplates">
                <div class="template-group">
                    <span class="template-group-label"><%= lang === 'ru' ? 'Структура' : 'Layout' %></span>
                    <button class="template-btn" data-insert="\\frac{}{}" data-mode="insert" title="<%= lang === 'ru' ? 'Дробь' : 'Fraction' %>">\(\frac{a}{b}\)</button>
                    <button class="template-btn" data-insert="\\sqrt{}" data-mode="insert" title="<%= lang === 'ru' ? 'Квадратный корень' : 'Square root' %>">\(\sqrt{x}\)</button>
                    <button class="template-btn" data-insert="\\sqrt[n]{}" data-mode="insert" title="<%= lang === 'ru' ? 'Корень n-й степени' : 'nth root' %>">\(\sqrt[n]{x}\)</button>
                    <button class="template-btn" data-insert="^{}" data-mode="insert" title="<%= lang === 'ru' ? 'Верхний индекс' : 'Superscript' %>">\(x^{n}\)</button>
                    <button class="template-btn" data-insert="_{}" data-mode="insert" title="<%= lang === 'ru' ? 'Нижний индекс' : 'Subscript' %>">\(x_{n}\)</button>
                    <button class="template-btn" data-insert="\\begin{pmatrix} a &amp; b \\\\ c &amp; d \\end{pmatrix}" data-mode="insert" title="<%= lang === 'ru' ? 'Матрица 2x2' : '2x2 Matrix' %>">\(\begin{pmatrix}a &amp; b \\ c &amp; d\end{pmatrix}\)</button>
                </div>
                <div class="template-group">
                    <span class="template-group-label"><%= lang === 'ru' ? 'Функции' : 'Functions' %></span>
                    <button class="template-btn" data-insert="\\sin " data-mode="insert" title="<%= lang === 'ru' ? 'Синус' : 'Sine' %>">\(\sin\)</button>
                    <button class="template-btn" data-insert="\\cos " data-mode="insert" title="<%= lang === 'ru' ? 'Косинус' : 'Cosine' %>">\(\cos\)</button>
                    <button class="template-btn" data-insert="\\tan " data-mode="insert" title="<%= lang === 'ru' ? 'Тангенс' : 'Tangent' %>">\(\tan\)</button>
                    <button class="template-btn" data-insert="\\arctan " data-mode="insert" title="<%= lang === 'ru' ? 'Арктангенс' : 'Arctangent' %>">\(\arctan\)</button>
                    <button class="template-btn" data-insert="\\ln " data-mode="insert" title="<%= lang === 'ru' ? 'Натуральный логарифм' : 'Natural logarithm' %>">\(\ln\)</button>
                    <button class="template-btn" data-insert="\\log " data-mode="insert" title="<%= lang === 'ru' ? 'Логарифм' : 'Logarithm' %>">\(\log\)</button>
                    <button class="template-btn" data-insert="\\lim_{x \\to a}" data-mode="insert" title="<%= lang === 'ru' ? 'Предел' : 'Limit' %>">\(\lim_{x \to a}\)</button>
                </div>
                <div class="template-group">
                    <span class="template-group-label"><%= lang === 'ru' ? 'Анализ' : 'Calculus' %></span>
                    <button class="template-btn" data-insert="\\frac{d }{d t}" data-mode="insert" title="<%= lang === 'ru' ? 'Производная' : 'Derivative' %>">\(\frac{d}{dt}\)</button>
                    <button class="template-btn" data-insert="\\frac{\\partial}{\\partial x}" data-mode="insert" title="<%= lang === 'ru' ? 'Частная производная' : 'Partial derivative' %>">\(\frac{\partial}{\partial x}\)</button>
                    <button class="template-btn" data-insert="\\int_{a}^{b} f(x)\\,dx" data-mode="insert" title="<%= lang === 'ru' ? 'Определённый интеграл' : 'Definite integral' %>">\(\int_{a}^{b}\)</button>
                    <button class="template-btn" data-insert="\\oint" data-mode="insert" title="<%= lang === 'ru' ? 'Контурный интеграл' : 'Contour integral' %>">\(\oint\)</button>
                    <button class="template-btn" data-insert="\\sum_{i=1}^{N}" data-mode="insert" title="<%= lang === 'ru' ? 'Сумма' : 'Summation' %>">\(\sum_{i=1}^{N}\)</button>
                </div>
                <div class="template-group">
                    <span class="template-group-label"><%= lang === 'ru' ? 'Обозначения' : 'Notation' %></span>
                    <button class="template-btn" data-insert="\\vec{}" data-mode="insert" title="<%= lang === 'ru' ? 'Вектор' : 'Vector' %>">\(\vec{F}\)</button>
                    <button class="template-btn" data-insert="\\times" data-mode="insert" title="<%= lang === 'ru' ? 'Векторное произведение' : 'Cross product' %>">\(\times\)</button>
                    <button class="template-btn" data-insert="\\cdot" data-mode="insert" title="<%= lang === 'ru' ? 'Скалярное произведение' : 'Dot product' %>">\(\cdot\)</button>
                    <button class="template-btn" data-insert="\\infty" data-mode="insert" title="<%= lang === 'ru' ? 'Бесконечность' : 'Infinity' %>">\(\infty\)</button>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Symbols section (full-width tabbed bar) -->
        <div class="template-section">
            <div class="symbols-section" id="symbolsSection">
                <div class="symbols-header">
                    <div class="symbols-tabs" id="symbolsTabs">
                        <button class="symbols-tab active" data-tab="greek"><%= lang === 'ru' ? 'Греческие' : 'Greek' %></button>
                        <button class="symbols-tab" data-tab="arrows"><%= lang === 'ru' ? 'Стрелки' : 'Arrows' %></button>
                        <button class="symbols-tab" data-tab="operators"><%= lang === 'ru' ? 'Операторы' : 'Operators' %></button>
                        <button class="symbols-tab" data-tab="relations"><%= lang === 'ru' ? 'Отношения' : 'Relations' %></button>
                        <button class="symbols-tab" data-tab="delimiters"><%= lang === 'ru' ? 'Скобки' : 'Delimiters' %></button>
                        <button class="symbols-tab" data-tab="logic"><%= lang === 'ru' ? 'Логика' : 'Logic' %></button>
                        <button class="symbols-tab" data-tab="accents"><%= lang === 'ru' ? 'Акценты' : 'Accents' %></button>
                        <button class="symbols-tab" data-tab="misc"><%= lang === 'ru' ? 'Прочее' : 'Misc' %></button>
                    </div>
                    <button class="symbols-collapse-btn" id="symbolsCollapseBtn" title="<%= lang === 'ru' ? 'Свернуть символы' : 'Collapse symbols' %>">
                        <svg width="12" height="7" viewBox="0 0 12 7" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round"><path d="M1 1l5 5 5-5"/></svg>
                    </button>
                </div>
                <div class="symbols-grid-wrap" id="symbolsGridWrap">
                        <div class="symbols-grid" id="symbols-greek">
                            <button class="symbol-btn" data-insert="\\alpha" data-mode="insert">&#x1D6FC;</button>
                            <button class="symbol-btn" data-insert="\\beta" data-mode="insert">&#x1D6FD;</button>
                            <button class="symbol-btn" data-insert="\\gamma" data-mode="insert">&#x1D6FE;</button>
                            <button class="symbol-btn" data-insert="\\delta" data-mode="insert">&#x1D6FF;</button>
                            <button class="symbol-btn" data-insert="\\varepsilon" data-mode="insert">&#x1D700;</button>
                            <button class="symbol-btn" data-insert="\\zeta" data-mode="insert">&#x1D701;</button>
                            <button class="symbol-btn" data-insert="\\eta" data-mode="insert">&#x1D702;</button>
                            <button class="symbol-btn" data-insert="\\theta" data-mode="insert">&#x1D703;</button>
                            <button class="symbol-btn" data-insert="\\iota" data-mode="insert">&#x1D704;</button>
                            <button class="symbol-btn" data-insert="\\ell" data-mode="insert">&#x2113;</button>
                            <button class="symbol-btn" data-insert="\\kappa" data-mode="insert">&#x1D705;</button>
                            <button class="symbol-btn" data-insert="\\lambda" data-mode="insert">&#x1D706;</button>
                            <button class="symbol-btn" data-insert="\\mu" data-mode="insert">&#x1D707;</button>
                            <button class="symbol-btn" data-insert="\\nu" data-mode="insert">&#x1D708;</button>
                            <button class="symbol-btn" data-insert="\\xi" data-mode="insert">&#x1D709;</button>
                            <button class="symbol-btn" data-insert="\\pi" data-mode="insert">&#x1D70B;</button>
                            <button class="symbol-btn" data-insert="\\rho" data-mode="insert">&#x1D70C;</button>
                            <button class="symbol-btn" data-insert="\\sigma" data-mode="insert">&#x1D70E;</button>
                            <button class="symbol-btn" data-insert="\\tau" data-mode="insert">&#x1D70F;</button>
                            <button class="symbol-btn" data-insert="\\upsilon" data-mode="insert">&#x1D710;</button>
                            <button class="symbol-btn" data-insert="\\varphi" data-mode="insert">&#x1D711;</button>
                            <button class="symbol-btn" data-insert="\\chi" data-mode="insert">&#x1D712;</button>
                            <button class="symbol-btn" data-insert="\\psi" data-mode="insert">&#x1D713;</button>
                            <button class="symbol-btn" data-insert="\\omega" data-mode="insert">&#x1D714;</button>
                            <button class="symbol-btn" data-insert="\\epsilon" data-mode="insert">&#x03F5;</button>
                            <button class="symbol-btn" data-insert="\\vartheta" data-mode="insert">&#x03D1;</button>
                            <button class="symbol-btn" data-insert="\\phi" data-mode="insert">&#x03D5;</button>
                            <button class="symbol-btn" data-insert="\\varpi" data-mode="insert">&#x03D6;</button>
                            <button class="symbol-btn" data-insert="\\varrho" data-mode="insert">&#x03F1;</button>
                            <button class="symbol-btn" data-insert="\\varsigma" data-mode="insert">&#x03C2;</button>
                            <button class="symbol-btn" data-insert="\\digamma" data-mode="insert">&#x03DD;</button>
                            <button class="symbol-btn" data-insert="\\Gamma" data-mode="insert">&Gamma;</button>
                            <button class="symbol-btn" data-insert="\\Delta" data-mode="insert">&Delta;</button>
                            <button class="symbol-btn" data-insert="\\Theta" data-mode="insert">&Theta;</button>
                            <button class="symbol-btn" data-insert="\\Lambda" data-mode="insert">&Lambda;</button>
                            <button class="symbol-btn" data-insert="\\Xi" data-mode="insert">&Xi;</button>
                            <button class="symbol-btn" data-insert="\\Pi" data-mode="insert">&Pi;</button>
                            <button class="symbol-btn" data-insert="\\Sigma" data-mode="insert">&Sigma;</button>
                            <button class="symbol-btn" data-insert="\\Upsilon" data-mode="insert">&Upsilon;</button>
                            <button class="symbol-btn" data-insert="\\Phi" data-mode="insert">&Phi;</button>
                            <button class="symbol-btn" data-insert="\\Psi" data-mode="insert">&Psi;</button>
                            <button class="symbol-btn" data-insert="\\Omega" data-mode="insert">&Omega;</button>
                        </div>
                        <div class="symbols-grid" id="symbols-arrows" style="display:none">
                            <button class="symbol-btn" data-insert="\\leftarrow" data-mode="insert">&larr;</button>
                            <button class="symbol-btn" data-insert="\\rightarrow" data-mode="insert">&rarr;</button>
                            <button class="symbol-btn" data-insert="\\leftrightarrow" data-mode="insert">&harr;</button>
                            <button class="symbol-btn" data-insert="\\uparrow" data-mode="insert">&uarr;</button>
                            <button class="symbol-btn" data-insert="\\downarrow" data-mode="insert">&darr;</button>
